channel.description:
[center][b]Z[/b] is a 562 revision-ed RuneScape Private Server that was founded and created by Drake. The project started on the [u]1st December 2013[/u] and was completed on [u]Christmas day 2013[/u]. The servers completion resulted to a big success in profit-making. Needless to say, Z holds a large amount of custom features.

[b]→Staff Positions[/b] Donator Moderator Head Moderator Administrator Head Administrator Co Owner
[size=10pt][b]Custom Features[/b][/size] Owner Zone Owner Zone Shop Staff Zone Shop Admin Zone Mod Zone Admin Zone Shop Mod Zone Shop Completionist Cape Drop Party Zone Advanced Bosses (Higher Than Corporeal Beast)[/center] +400 more
